data.description: Wow, this 2-Bd PLUS loft, 2.5-Bath home sparkles with pride of ownership! Popular floor plan with decorator touches. Great room opens to kitchen island, w/ Corian countertops, stainless appliances, custom tile backsplash, & pantry. Great room with surround sound built in speakers. One of the few with PRIVATE BRAND NEW POOL and spacious covered patio & private backyard. Master suite features double sinks, soaking tub, separate shower & walk-in closet. Ideal n/s facing, private, interior lot close to resort style community pool w/ beach entry, waterfall, huge hot tub, basketball court, & 2 community playgrounds. A gated community, close to highways, downtown Phoenix, shopping, & recreation
